al separation of electron and hole to\nopposite layers. These results lay the foundation for exploiting the interlayer\nexciton in future 2D heterostructure optoelectronic devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Jan 2017 19:52:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-05"}
