estrial water clouds but also in Jovian ice clouds. Our model will be\nuseful to understand how the dynamics, compositions, and nucleation processes\nin exoplanetary atmospheresaffects the vertical extent and optical thickness of\nexoplanetary clouds via cloud microphysics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jan 2017 07:10:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-08"}
