ew. Mathematically it is very\ninteresting to look at the consequences of the interplay between the \"actual\"\nand the \"possible\" and this is the aim of this short review.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Jan 2017 13:17:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-05"}
